[TranslatorEvent11]
Message="I have been hiding here for what seems like months now. The Skaarj forces that have taken over our monastery continue to transport stolen tarydium and other strange mechanical devices using their lightning sled. I fear that they may find me."

[TranslatorEvent8]
Message="MAGNETIC LOCKS ENGAGED: AUTHORIZED BY CAPTAIN DUK'CHOROTH - OF THE 12th HOUSE OF dUBREVI"
