[TranslatorEvent18]
Message="Acolyte Ne'Pher Dunis 350-488"

[TranslatorEvent14]
Message="The woman they captured is scheduled to be executed. I cannot let this happen! As foolish as it sounds I will attempt to sneak her out of the prison cell through our secret caves. From there she can escape to the bell tower until darkness."

[TranslatorEvent5]
Message="SKAARJ SHIPPING FACILITY POWER MANAGEMENT STATION: HYDRO-ELECTRIC SHIPPING CAR STATUS - OFF / REACTIVATION REQUIRES STATIC DISCHARGE NODES TO BE OPENED AT TOP OF BELL TOWER."

[TranslatorEvent10]
Message="HAVE FAITH AND NEVER SWAY FROM YOUR BELIEFS. ONLY A SOUL THAT KEEPS THE FAITH DESPITE ALL OPPRESSION SHALL TRIUMPH WHEN THE SAVIOUR PRINCESS COMES FROM THE STARS"

[TranslatorEvent13]
Message="Myscha Nov 28th 1994- June 1997"

[TranslatorEvent19]
Message="I am feeling ill. My cough has gotten worse and this darkened cell is not helping. I only hope that my  brother Kruun can escape to our childhood hiding hole in the sewers. From there he can access the inner walls of the monastery."

[TranslatorEvent1]
Message="Security Officer Sergai Dubrov: ISV-KRAN: LOG ENTRY: We are hot on the trail of the Skaarj Hunting party that captured Kira near the Sunspire. They are headed north towards the blue electrical storms on the horizon."

[TranslatorEvent12]
Message="I have discovered a secret! Last night I snuck out of my hiding place and swam through the pipes to the prison. They have captured a Girl! The Krall sergeant took two boots in the mouth when he approached her. Haha! I can only laugh at their stupidity."

[TranslatorEvent22]
Message="Son of Ne'Lin Garas 380-390"

[TranslatorEvent23]
Message="Pelit Jan 20 1997-July 17 1997"

[TranslatorEvent17]
Message="Only by facing the direction of the rising sun may one find a new day."

