AltMessage="HYDRO-LASER CONTROL STATION: LASERS DISENGAGED - ACCESS TO HYDRO-ELECTRIC GENERATOR BELOW BELL TOWER PERMITTED"

[TranslatorEvent3]
Message="My brother Kriin is in the cell below me. My other brother Kruun escaped through the water tunnel under the stairs. They sacrificed my best friend Jaara for Kruun's escape."

[TranslatorEvent15]
Message="Vault of the Dead - Herein lies the last resting place of the High Priest of Bluff Eversmoking and the artifacts used by the Messiah."
Hint="Find a secret lever in the graveyard"

[TranslatorEvent2]
Message="Science Officer Kira Argmanov: Separated from my crewmates from ISV-KRAN, I've only been able to stay alive by holding up in this bell tower. A native Nali help me escape the prison cell the Skaarj put me in. Hopefully the Skaarj won't find me here."

[TranslatorEvent0]
Message="ISV-KRAN Chief Medical Officer Log: Tatiana Zimna: We have come to this beautiful canyon lake monastery in our search for Kira's abductors. We'll make camp by this crucifix tonight and start out early tomorrow."

[TranslatorEvent26]
Message="Shipping Log: Grorq of the Red Hand Tribe. I am really getting sick with the way the Skaarj are treating us. Constantly bossing us around and making us watch over their pathetic Nali slaves. My troops are getting sick of this situation."

[TranslatorEvent24]
Message="Shipping Log: Grorq of the Red Hand Tribe. Coming the next full moon we are expecting a large shipment of salvaged supplies from the human spacecraft. I need to make a few repairs to the electric rails around the bluff but we should be ready by then."

[TranslatorEvent25]
Message="Jailer Hrang of the Red Hand Tribe: we have captured a Terran girl. Some of my soldiers want to try and take liberties with her. I guess that's OK as long as they watch those boots! She kicked me in the Hrangos last time."

[TranslatorEvent27]
Message="Jailer Hrang of the Red Hand Tribe: Dorro owes me 25,000 gold Paaras when we get home! He truly sucks at death bones. Hustling him is like taking candy from a Terran baby. Speaking of which I think it's time to go beat on that ugly Terran girl some more!"

[TranslatorEvent28]
Message="Jailer Hrang of the Red Hand Tribe: I can't believe it!!! That Terran girl escaped! One of those worthless Nali Monks must have tunneled her out. I am in DEEP SHIT! If Captain DUK'CHOROTH comes and finds out I let her escape I'll be de-hrangod for sure!"

[TranslatorEvent29]
Message="Kruun's personal diary: I have to be careful how many times I sneak into the monastery through the tunnels. I've marked the tunnel that leads to the inner monastery with a cross, the other leads to the prison where my brother is still being held."

